body_html: Figured it out. There are several horrible mistakes in that code. First off, you're not supposed to create tensors outside the session context, second, those don't go into the feed dictionary anyway, from what I gathered, third, I confused JavaScript object notation with Python dictionary syntax, causing me to use PCM frames rather than placeholders from the graph as feed keys. Humiliating. Ouch.
